title: Relates to eliminating the requirement that copies of the report of independent medical examination must be submitted to all parties in the same manner
summary: Relates to eliminating the requirement that copies of the report of independent medical examination must be submitted to all parties in the same manner.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the workers' compensation law, in relation to eliminating the requirement that copies of the report of independent medical examination must be submitted to all parties in the same manner
